ider.com%2Fmom-doesnt-do-birthday-parties-after-first-year-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebirthday%20parties%20at%20my%20house%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20taking%20my%20friends%20down%20to%20our%20basement%20to%20see%20my%20mom's%20huge%20collection%20of%20tiny%20figures%2C%20neatly%20organised%20in%20typeset%20trays%20hanging%20all%20over%20the%20walls.%20Our%20entire%201000-square-foot%20basement%20had%20been%20turned%20into%20a%20sort%20of%20antique%20warehouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20started%20when%20my%20mom%20was%2014%2C%20in%20the%20early%2070s.%20Her%20friend%20had%20been%20given%20a%20typeset%20tray%20and%20put%20little%20items%20in%20it.%20My%20mom%20wanted%20to%20do%20the%20same%2C%20so%20she%20went%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgarage-sale-millionaire-flipped-tin-toy-for-thousands-2016-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egarage%20sale%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20found%20a%20tray%20like%20the%20one%20her%20friend%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20woman%20on%20cork%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a0b5421fb3fcb426488963%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECelina%20Myers's%20mom%20started%20buying%20miniatures%20with%20the%20%242%20her%20aunt%20would%20give%20her%20for%20her%20birthday.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Celina%20Myers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20birthday%2C%20her%20aunts%20would%20gift%20her%20%242%20to%20buy%20a%20charm%20for%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgetting-permanent-bracelet-fun-alternative-to-tattoos-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echarm%20bracele%3C%2Fa%3Et%2C%20but%20instead%20of%20buying%20a%20charm%2C%20Mom%20would%20buy%20a%20miniature%20for%20her%20tray.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20after%20another%2C%20typeset%20trays%20filled.%20And%20this%20is%20still%20happening%20even%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22be8de1c8-b88f-448b-acfc-6ac854eeca5c%5C%22%3EMy%20friends%20love%20to%20see%20the%20collection%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20kid%2C%20my%20friends%20loved%20coming%20to%20our%20house%20because%20they%20wanted%20to%20see%20the%20collection%20in%20the%20basement.%20They%20all%20jumped%20from%20hole%20to%20hole%20to%20see%20what%20new%20miniature%20she%20had%20added%20most%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20personal%20favorites%20were%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvaluable-things-from-the-90s-worth-money-a-fortune-today%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpice%20Girls%20dolls%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20crazy%20bones%2C%20and%20old%20playing%20cards.%20I%20loved%20the%20nostalgic%20ones%20most%2C%20the%20ones%20I%20remember%20buying%20with%20mom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20mom%20never%20stopped%20us%20from%20looking%20at%20her%20special%20finds%2C%20she%20always%20said%20that%20we%20had%20to%20look%20with%20our%20eyes%20and%20not%20touch%20with%20our%20fingers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Miniature%20collection%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a0b49ffd4fbd083f2923f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECelina%20Myers'%20mom%20collected%20miniatures%20for%2050%20years.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Celina%20Myers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20never%20occurred%20to%20me%20that%20her%20collection%20was%20weird.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20thought%20she%20was%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhad-chill-mom-relaxed-parent-growing-up-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereally%20cool%20mom%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20everyone%20loved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20Saturday%2C%20my%20mom%2C%20grandma%2C%20and%20I%20would%20head%20out%20to%20the%20garage%20sales%20to%20find%20new%20additions.%20We%20called%20ourselves%20the%20Three%20Musketeers.%20We'd%20scan%20all%20the%20knickknacks%20to%20see%20what%20we%20liked%2C%20what%20we%20didn't%20have%2C%20and%20what%20would%20fit%20in%20the%20typeset%20box%20compartments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMom%20also%20went%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-thrift-shop-in-every-state-yelp-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eantique%20shops%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I'd%20add%20my%20own%20Happy%20Meal%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20family%20adventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8f3766f-7ab9-4650-a770-c556dc4b1d74%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20collecting%2C%20not%20hoarding%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20never%20got%20rid%20of%20anything%2C%20but%20I%20wouldn't%20call%20this%20hoarding.%20I'd%20call%20it%20collecting%2C%20because%20she%20displayed%20everything%20beautifully%2C%20always%20making%20sure%20the%20miniatures%20were%20dusted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20think%20about%20the%20future%20of%20clearing%20out%20this%20space%20when%20she's%20no%20longer%20with%20us%2C%20I%20sometimes%20feel%20intimidated.%20But%20she%20finds%20so%20much%20joy%20in%20her%20collection%2C%20and%20I%20wouldn't%20ever%20want%20to%20ask%20her%20to%20downsize%20what%20she%20has%20on%20display.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Miniature%20collection%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a0b583d3e2f1aef3699bf6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECelina%20Myers%20says%20her%20mom%20still%20feels%20joy%20looking%20at%20her%20collection.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Celina%20Myers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20told%20her%20that%20one%20day%2C%20I%20want%20to%20open%20a%20museum%20or%20a%20breakfast%20restaurant%20with%20her%20collection%20behind%20Plexiglas.%20I'd%20call%20it%20Joanne's.%20Everyone%20can%20enjoy%20it%20then%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20what%20she%20wants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20miniature%20is%20a%20piece%20of%20my%20mom%20that%20means%20so%20much%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff343b76-456a-4857-b3f3-35411ebb5cea%5C%22%3EShe%20still%20finds%20joy%20in%20her%20collection%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20she's%20become%20severely%20disabled%2C%20and%20one%20of%20her%20greatest%20joys%20throughout%20has%20been%20describing%20exactly%20where%20and%20when%20she%20found%20a%20particular%20miniature%2C%20and%20the%20story%20behind%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20she%20can't%20get%20out%20easily%20to%20garage%20sales%20and%20antique%20stores%20to%20find%20miniatures%20now%20that%20she%20is%20in%20a%20wheelchair%2C%20she%20loves%20using%20Facebook%20Marketplace%20and%20Craigslist.%20She'll%20find%20something%20she%20wants%20online%2C%20and%20Dad%20will%20pack%20up%20the%20wheelchair%2C%20and%20off%20they%20go%20to%20collect%20the%20knickknack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Miniature%20collection%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a0b793fd4fbd083f292470%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECelina%20Myers%20is%20thinking%20about%20setting%20up%20a%20P.O.%20Box%20so%20people%20can%20send%20miniatures%20to%20her%20mom.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Celina%20Myers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I%20posted%20a%20video%20of%20her%20collection%20on%20Instagram%2C%20there%20were%2012%2C000%20comments%2C%20and%20mom%20wanted%20to%20read%20each%20one.%20She%20loved%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20planning%20to%20open%20a%20PO%20Box%20and%20then%20post%20a%20YouTube%20video%20asking%20people%20to%20send%20her%20collectibles%2C%20along%20with%20a%20note%20explaining%20the%20item%20and%20its%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20she'll%20sit%20for%20hours%2C%20looking%20at%20what's%20been%20sent%20to%20her%20and%20enjoying%20the%20letters%20that%20accompany%20it.%20It%20will%20light%20her%20up%2C%20make%20her%20so%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-50-year-miniature-collection-basement-viral-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772915281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a0b44cfd4fbd083f2923ed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-50-year-miniature-collection-basement-viral-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20mom%20has%20spent%2050%20years%20collecting%20miniatures%20that%20now%20fill%20our%20entire%20basement.%20She%20didn't%20get%20rid%20of%20any%20and%20my%20friends%20loved%20coming%20to%20look%20at%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Lauren%20Crosby%20Medlicott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-50-year-miniature-collection-basement-viral-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Southwest%20flight%20diverted%20mid-air%20over%20'possible%20security%20matter'%3B%20FBI%20confirms%20no%20threat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772914648000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129233145%2Cimgsize-61196.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fsouthwest-flight-diverted-mid-air-over-possible-security-matter-fbi-confirms-no-threat%2Farticleshow%2F129233145.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F129233145.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fsouthwest-flight-diverted-mid-air-over-possible-security-matter-fbi-confirms-no-threat%2Farticleshow%2F129233145.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fsouthwest-flight-diverted-