.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fblaming-h-1bs-when-suspect-was-us-citizen-hindu-american-group-slams-texas-politicians-for-linking-austin-shooting-to-immigrants%2Famp_articleshow%2F129227415.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OpenAI's%20robotics%20head%20quits%20after%20company's%20Pentagon%20deal%3A%20'This%20was%20about%20principle'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Altman%20with%20a%20finger%20to%20his%20lips%2C%20wearing%20a%20suit%20in%20front%20of%20a%20black%20and%20orange%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699cacbd2237a6a8f0cdad6b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOpenAI%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman.%3Cp%3ENathan%20Howard%E2%80%94Bloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECaitlin%20Kalinowski%2C%20OpenAI's%20head%20of%20robotics%2C%20said%20on%20Saturday%20that%20she%20had%20resigned.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20an%20X%20post%2C%20she%20criticized%20OpenAI's%20deal%20with%20the%20Pentagon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20deal%20raised%20concerns%20over%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20surveillance%20and%20lethal%20autonomous%20systems.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECaitlin%20Kalinowski%2C%20a%20hardware%20executive%20who%20joined%20OpenAI%20from%20Meta%20in%202024%20and%20leads%20its%20robotics%20division%2C%20said%20she%20is%20resigning%20from%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Kalinowski%20criticized%20OpenAI's%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-pentagon-government-deal-controversy-explained-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edeal%20with%20the%20Pentagon%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20has%20an%20important%20role%20in%20national%20security.%20But%20surveillance%20of%20Americans%20without%20judicial%20oversight%20and%20lethal%20autonomy%20without%20human%20authorization%20are%20lines%20that%20deserved%20more%20deliberation%20than%20they%20got%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20called%20her%20resignation%20a%20matter%20of%20principle%2C%20and%20said%20she%20still%20deeply%20respects%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20and%20is%20proud%20of%20the%20company's%20robotics%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20OpenAI%20confirmed%20Kalinowski's%20resignation%20and%20defended%20its%20deal%20with%20the%20Defense%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20our%20agreement%20with%20the%20Pentagon%20creates%20a%20workable%20path%20for%20responsible%20national%20security%20uses%20of%20AI%20while%20making%20clear%20our%20red%20lines%3A%20no%20domestic%20surveillance%20and%20no%20autonomous%20weapons%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20recognize%20that%20people%20have%20strong%20views%20about%20these%20issues%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20engage%20in%20discussion%20with%20employees%2C%20government%2C%20civil%20society%2C%20and%20communities%20around%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20struck%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20Pentagon%20last%20week%2C%20allowing%20the%20Defense%20Department%20to%20use%20its%20AI%20products.%20The%20agreement%20came%20after%20its%20rival%20Anthropic%20refused%20a%20similar%20deal%20over%20concerns%20that%20the%20technology%20would%20be%20used%20for%20mass%20surveillance%20and%20autonomous%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWashington%20has%20since%20effectively%20blacklisted%20Anthropic.%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20described%20the%20company%20as%20%26quot%3Bradical%20woke%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post%20and%20demanded%20federal%20agencies%20stop%20using%20Anthropic's%20technology.%20Secretary%20of%20Defense%20Pete%20Hegseth%20then%20designated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-pentagon-government-deal-controversy-explained-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic%20a%20supply-chain%20risk%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20said%20Defense%20Department%20contractors%20would%20be%20barred%20from%20working%20with%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20decision%20to%20strike%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20Pentagon%20caused%20an%20immediate%20backlash.%20Some%20users%20ditched%20ChatGPT%20in%20protest.%20Anthropic's%20chatbot%2C%20Claude%2C%20is%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-number-1-app-stores-chatgpt-apple-google-ai-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20No.%201%20free%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Apple%20App%20Store%2C%20unseating%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT.%20Claude's%20US%20downloads%20increased%20240%25%20month%20over%20month%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalinowski's%20exit%20is%20a%20setback%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopen-ai-robotics-lab-humanoid-robots-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20robotics%3C%2Fa%3E%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20year%2C%20the%20company%20has%20quietly%20built%20a%20San%20Francisco%20lab%20that%20employs%20about%20100%20data%20collectors.%20Teams%20are%20training%20a%20robotic%20arm%20to%20do%20household%20chores%20as%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20push%20to%20build%20a%20humanoid%20robot.%20The%20company%20told%20employees%20in%20December%20it%20also%20plans%20to%20open%20a%20second%20lab%20in%20Richmond%2C%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20source%20with%20knowledge%20of%20OpenAI's%20plans%20also%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20company%20is%20exploring%20several%20early-stage%20hardware%20initiatives%20%E2%80%94%20including%20robotics%20%E2%80%94%20but%20none%20are%20considered%20central%20to%20its%20core%20mission%20at%20this%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaitlin-kalinowski-quits-openai-robotics-head-pentagon-deal-sam-altman-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published