2921d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22779%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELuana%20Ribeira%20and%20her%20partner%20live%20in%20separate%20houses.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Luana%20Ribeira%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELuana%20Ribeira%20has%20been%20with%20her%20partner%20since%202017%2C%20and%20they%20share%20a%20son.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20lived%20together%20initially%2C%20but%20moved%20into%20separate%20houses%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20says%20the%20arrangement%20allows%20each%20family%20member%20to%20have%20time%20to%20themselves.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3ELuana%20Ribeira%3Cem%3E%2C%20founder%20of%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdauntlesspr.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDauntless%20PR%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELittle%20about%20my%20relationship%20with%20Al%20is%20traditional.%20For%20starters%2C%20Al%20was%20my%20former%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-best-friend-platonic-life-partner-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehusband's%20best%20friend%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20divorced%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Portugal%2C%20where%20Al%20was%20living.%20I%20was%20planning%20on%20spending%20time%20with%20Al%20as%20a%20friend%2C%20but%20the%20second%20time%20we%20hung%20out%2C%20he%20called%20my%20ex%20to%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BThere's%20something%20here.%26quot%3B%20Luckily%2C%20my%20ex%20gave%20his%20blessing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20dating%20Al%20soon%20after%2C%20in%202017.%20In%202020%2C%20we%20moved%20to%20the%20UK%2C%20where%20I'm%20from.%20That's%20when%20we%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-been-together-for-6-years-never-slept-same-bed-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20separate%20bedrooms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20both%20were%20having%20trouble%20sleeping%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20enjoyed%20having%20our%20own%20space.%20We%20had%20a%20spare%20room%2C%20so%20Al%20started%20sleeping%20in%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20we%20wanted%20even%20more%20space%20from%20each%20other.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20my%20two%20teenage%20daughters%20were%20living%20with%20us%2C%20and%20the%20house%20was%20loud.%20Al%20craved%20quiet%2C%20and%20that%20was%20fine%20with%20me%20%E2%80%94%20I%20wanted%20him%20to%20take%20care%20of%20himself.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flive-small-mobile-home-independence-freedom-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econverted%20an%20existing%20warehouse%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20our%20property%20into%20a%20bedsit%20(similar%20to%20a%20studio%20apartment).%20He%20slept%20there%20and%20used%20it%20when%20he%20needed%20quiet%20time%20to%20create%20art%20or%20watch%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228147fa76-f0d6-4fb3-9e16-408a0d3f2576%5C%22%3EWe%20wanted%20different%20settings%20for%20our%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20June%2C%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-florida-to-portugal-better-cost-of-living-for-family-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20back%20to%20Portugal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20our%204-year-old%20son%2C%20Celyn.%20By%20that%20point%20in%20our%20relationship%2C%20Al%20and%20I%20recognized%20that%20we%20live%20completely%20opposite%20lifestyles%20at%20home.%20I%20like%20creature%20comforts%20and%20wanted%20my%20dream%20lakeside%20home%20in%20Portugal.%20Al%20was%20interested%20in%20becoming%20even%20more%20self-sufficient%2C%20living%20off-grid%20if%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAl%20already%20owned%20about%20an%20acre%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-moved-florida-southern-portugal-better-life-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eland%20in%20Portugal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20put%20a%20yurt%20on%20the%20land%2C%20and%20now%20lives%20there%20without%20running%20water%20and%20with%20only%20limited%20solar%20power.%20The%20one%20modern%20amenity%20I%20insisted%20on%20was%20wifi%2C%20so%20I%20can%20get%20a%20hold%20of%20him%20and%20Celyn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20meanwhile%20rent%20a%20two-bedroom%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolorado-mansion-with-100-car-garage-playboy-pool-for-sale-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehome%20with%20a%20pool%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20can%20see%20a%20nearby%20lake%20from%20my%20windows.%20I'm%20still%20in%20a%20rural%20area%2C%20but%20nowhere%20near%20as%20rural%20as%20Al.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223e0714ce-2a73-4288-a86f-3d72992460b7%5C%22%3EWe%20follow%20a%20strict%20weekly%20schedule%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-for-coordinating-family-schedules-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehave%20a%20family%20schedule%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20might%20look%20familiar%20to%20separated%20parents%2C%20though%20Al%20and%20I%20are%20very%20much%20together.%20On%20Sunday%20nights%2C%20Al%20and%20Celyn%20go%20to%20the%20yurt.%20I%20work%20long%20days%20on%20Monday%20and%20Tuesday%2C%20and%20also%20have%20time%20to%20swim%20and%20make%20any%20appointments%20I%20need%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20I%20pick%20Celyn%20up.%20That's%20my%20favorite%20part%20of%20the%20week%2C%20seeing%20him%20run%20down%20the%20lane%20toward%20me.%20I%20have%20Celyn%20on%20my%20own%20until%20Friday%20night%2C%20when%20Al%20comes%20to%20spend%20the%20weekend%20with%20us.%20That%20family%20time%20always%20happens%20at%20my%20house%2C%20since%20it's%20more%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdigital-detox-weekend-without-screens-helped-my-family-teen-reconnect-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eweekends%20as%20a%20family%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20sacred%20to%20us.%20It's%20also%20nice%20to%20have%20one-on-one%20time%20with%20our%20son%20and%20to%20have%20alone%20time%20built%20into%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a2272499-a37d-4c8d-bdc6-efc11fa6e232%5C%22%3EThis%20arrangement%20lets%20us%20be%20ourselves%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20homes%20are%20about%2050%20minutes%20apart%20right%20now.%20If%20something%20pops%20up%20with%20work%2C%20I%20can't%20just%20send%20Celyn%20to%20his%20dad's%20on%20a%20whim.%20Sometimes%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20driving%20all%20the%20time%2C%20so%20I'll%20probably%20move%20closer%20to%20Al%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinancially%2C%20there's%20not%20a%20huge%20expense%20involved%20with%20having%20two%20homes.%20Al%20already%20owned%20his%20land.%20I'm%20the%20sole%20earner%20in%20our%20relationship%2C%20so%20I%20bought%20the%20yurt%2C%20and%20I%20finance%20projects%20on%20the%20land%20as%20they%20come%20up.%20Luckily%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20bills%20with%20an%20off-grid%20homestead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20this%20isn't%20for%20everyone%2C%20but%20I'm%20glad%20that%20Al%20and%20I%20can%20do%20what's%20right%20for%20us.%20We%20want%20to%20support%20each%20other%2C%20and%20don't%20want%20to%20ask%20our%20partner%20to%20change%20who%20they%20are.%20Living%20apart%20gives%20us%20the%20space%20we%20need%20to%20be%20ourselves%2C%20while%20still%20being%20a%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-living-apart-separate-homes-relationship-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772905141000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a0a4431fb3fcb426488730%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-living-apart-separate-homes-relationship-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20partner%20lives%20off-grid%20in%20a%20yurt%20while%20I%20rent%20a%20lakeside%20home.%20Living%20apart%20has%20strengthened%20our%20relationship.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%