%20center%20on%20board%20the%20USS%20New%20Jersey%20features%20a%20Tomahawk%20Weapons%20System.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20those%20are%20contemporary%20systems%2C%20to%20be%20able%20to%20see%20a%20Tomahawk%20missile%2C%20to%20be%20able%20to%20see%20Tomahawk%20missile%20launchers%20in%20a%20museum%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20museum%20ships%20like%20us%20that%20you%20could%20come%20and%20see%20to%20get%20that%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Szimanski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20ships%20even%20offer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubmarine-airbnb-photos-world-war-ii-museum-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esleepover%20experiences%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20guests%20can%20eat%20meals%20in%20the%20crew's%20mess%20and%20spend%20the%20night%20in%20sailors'%20bunks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20highly%20unlikely%20that%20the%20average%20person%20will%20get%20the%20chance%20to%20visit%20an%20active-duty%20Navy%20ship%2C%26quot%3B%20Szimanski%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20to%20experience%20the%20conditions%2C%20to%20see%20what%20it's%20like%20to%20serve%20on%20a%20warship%2C%20particularly%20one%20that%20has%20seen%20combat%2C%20visiting%20a%20museum%20ship%20is%20your%20best%20chance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224f92e0f7-7700-4341-bcb0-cce5fe24f95d%5C%22%3E'Remarkably%20similar'%20to%20modern%20Navy%20ships%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20USS%20Torsk%20in%20Baltimore.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab2d4f1fb3fcb42649154a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20USS%20Torsk%20submarine%20in%20Baltimore.%3Cp%3EVacclav%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20technologies%20and%20configurations%20found%20in%20World%20War%20II%20submarines%20may%20be%20outdated%2C%20many%20aspects%20of%20how%20they%20operate%20remain%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20the%20Navy%2C%20the%20military%2C%20all%20of%20us%2C%20operate%20in%20a%20world%20governed%20by%20laws%20of%20physics%2C%20and%20so%20there%20are%20some%20things%20that%20are%20just%20never%20going%20to%20change%20in%20how%20submarines%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Auer%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20walk%20through%20a%20modern%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrikes-iran-showed-value-stealthy-subs-launching-lots-of-missiles-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOhio-class%2C%20ballistic%20missile%20submarine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20find%20things%20that%20are%20exactly%20the%20same%2C%20or%20done%20exactly%20the%20same%20way%2C%20on%20the%20USS%20Torsk.%20And%20what%20we%20can%20really%20show%20is%20where%20those%20things%20were%20first%20done%2C%20and%20why%20they%20were%20done%20that%20way%2C%20and%20why%20they%20are%20still%20done%20that%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EModern%20submarines%20still%20appear%20%26quot%3Bremarkably%20similar%26quot%3B%20to%20their%20museum%20counterparts%2C%20Szimanski%20said.%20The%20layout%20of%20submarines%20hasn't%20changed%20all%20that%20much%20since%20World%20War%20II.%20They%20largely%20still%20have%20the%20same%20spaces%20to%20eat%2C%20sleep%2C%20and%20fire%20torpedoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuer%20says%20that%20when%20he%20leads%20tours%20of%20the%20USS%20Torsk%20for%20active-duty%20sailors%2C%20he%20often%20gets%20the%20response%2C%20%26quot%3BHuh%2C%20we're%20still%20doing%20it%20this%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20forward%20torpedo%20room%20inside%20the%20USS%20Torsk%20submarine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab26391fb3fcb426491430%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20forward%20torpedo%20room%20inside%20the%20USS%20Torsk.%3Cp%3EPixel%20Doc%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20differences%20can%20be%20found%20in%20the%20ships'%20capabilities%2C%20Hugh%20McKeever%2C%20the%20shipboard%20education%20manager%20at%20the%20Independence%20Seaport%20Museum%20in%20Philadelphia%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiesel-powered%20submarines%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnavy-submarine-tour-world-war-ii-becuna-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUSS%20Becuna%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20sank%203%2C888%20tons%20of%20shipping%20in%20World%20War%20II%20before%20arriving%20at%20the%20Independence%20Seaport%20Museum%2C%20had%20to%20spend%20most%20of%20their%20time%20on%20the%20surface%20with%20only%20about%2012%20hours'%20worth%20of%20oxygen%20at%20a%20time.%20Today's%20nuclear-powered%20submarines%20operate%20with%20an%20unlimited%20fuel%20supply%20and%20can%20stay%20submerged%20for%20upward%20of%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20going%20out%20to%20sea%2C%20their%20ability%20is%20pretty%20much%20limited%20only%20by%20food%2C%26quot%3B%20McKeever%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20World%20War%20II-era%20submarines%20are%20less%20antiquated%20than%20one%20might%20assume.%20Some%20even%20still%20work.%20The%20USS%20Torsk's%20sister%20ship%2C%20the%20USS%20Cutlass%2C%20was%20commissioned%20in%201945%2C%20sold%20to%20Taiwan%20in%201973%2C%20and%20remains%20operational%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Republic%20of%20China%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20boats%2C%20to%20us%2C%20are%20so%20outdated%20that%20they're%20museums%2C%20but%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%20they're%20relatively%20advanced%2C%26quot%3B%20Auer%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20still%20very%20capable%20of%20doing%20the%20function%20they%20were%20originally%20designed%20for.%20So%2C%20were%20they%20implemented%20by%20some%20foreign%20threat%2C%20they%20would%20be%20a%20threat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22524720e9-ad17-4c0c-8156-5dce5b425409%5C%22%3EFloating%20museums%20find%20new%20relevance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22764%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20USS%20Becuna%2C%20a%20World%20War%20II%20submarine%2C%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Independence%20Seaport%20Museum%20in%20Philadelphia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a9ccdefd4fbd083f299870%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22509%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20USS%20Becuna%2C%20a%20World%20War%20II%20submarine%2C%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Independence%20Seaport%20Museum%20in%20Philadelphia.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20ship%20museum%20curators%2C%20the%20resurgence%20of%20naval%20battles%20in%20the%20US%20war%20with%20Iran%20underscores%20the%20contemporary%20relevance%20of%20World%20War%20II%20museum%20ships%20and%20the%20battle%20stars%20they%20earned.%20McKeever%2C%20for%20one%2C%20anticipates%20getting%20more%20questions%20about%20torpedoes%20as%20the%20summer%20tourist%20season%20ramps%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20US%20as%20a%20maritime%20power%2C%20the%20economic%20prosperity%20of%20the%20country%20is%20tied%20to%20the%20sea%20and%20the%20Navy%2C%26quot%3B%20McKeever%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20museum%20vessels%20represent%20that%20constant%20need%20for%20change%20and%20growth%20as%20a%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20as%20Szimanski%20noted%2C%20it%20was%20just%20days%20ago%20that%20no%20active%20US%20Navy%20ships%20had%20ever%20sunk%20an%20enemy%20warship%20%E2%80%94%20the%20only%20Navy%20ships%20that%20had%20fought%20a%20naval%20battle%20were%20all%20museum%20ships.%20Despite%20some%20rust%20and%20peeling%20paint%2C%20it%20seems%20they%20still%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20teach%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fww2-museum-ships-submari