past%20December%2C%20I%20took%20the%20kids%20on%20a%20trip%20to%20Philadelphia%20and%20New%20York%20City.%20This%20was%20our%20first%20big%20flight%20together.%20During%20my%20trip%20preparations%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20minors%20aren't%20required%20to%20have%20IDs%20when%20traveling%20with%20adults.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ad5111c1-d1e1-4d00-aece-015a86a1311f%5C%22%3EEven%20though%20IDs%20weren't%20technically%20required%2C%20this%20wasn't%20a%20risk%20I%20was%20willing%20to%20take%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20made%20sure%20each%20of%20the%20boys%20took%20their%20passports%20on%20this%20trip%2C%20which%20was%20a%20good%20call%20because%20the%20TSA%20agents%20asked%20to%20see%20their%20IDs%20each%20time%20we%20went%20through%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20know%20what%20would%20have%20happened%20if%20they%20didn't%20have%20their%20documents%20with%20them%2C%20but%20I'm%20glad%20we%20didn't%20find%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20super%20Type%20A%20and%20like%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%20worst-case%20scenarios%2C%20which%20is%20why%20I%20prioritized%20bringing%20these%20documents%20with%20me%20on%20our%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20we%20went%20on%20our%20holiday%2C%20I%20found%20a%20generic%20travel%20consent%20form%20online%20and%20had%20each%20kid's%20parent%20fill%20one%20out%20for%20their%20child.%20Then%20we%20went%20to%20get%20the%20documents%20notarized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20documents%20outlined%20our%20travel%20dates%20and%20destinations%2C%20so%20if%20any%20officials%20ever%20asked%20to%20see%20them%2C%20they're%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20brought%20the%20birth%20certificate%20copies%20as%20a%20double%20layer%20of%20security%20to%20prove%20that%20the%20people%20who%20filled%20out%20the%20consent%20forms%20are%20actually%20the%20kids'%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20might%20think%20this%20is%20excessive.%20I%20think%20it's%20wise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a875c783-74c6-4065-983f-e5dcf0c2f925%5C%22%3EThankfully%2C%20nobody%20asked%20to%20see%20these%20documents%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20imagine%20a%20scenario%20when%20a%20flight%20attendant%20or%20TSA%20agent%20would%20want%20to%20see%20such%20detailed%20proof%20of%20our%20travel%20plans%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20a%20chance%20I'm%20willing%20to%20take.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20taking%20a%20family%20cruise%20later%20this%20year%2C%20and%20the%20agent%20I%20spoke%20with%20during%20booking%20told%20me%20I'd%20need%20to%20fill%20out%20a%20travel%20consent%20form%20for%20each%20child%20before%20we%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20emailed%20the%20form%20to%20me%20before%20we%20finished%20our%20call%2C%20which%20I%20really%20appreciated.%20I've%20worked%20in%20the%20cruise%20industry%20before%2C%20so%20I%20know%20major%20cruise%20lines%20have%20their%20own%20versions%20of%20these%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20cruise%20with%20minors%20you%20don't%20have%20legal%20custody%20over%2C%20you%20have%20to%20fill%20out%20and%20submit%20these%20consent%20forms%20before%20embarkation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20my%20godkids%20and%20am%20so%20blessed%20to%20take%20them%20on%20trips.%20I%20want%20our%20vacations%20to%20be%20unforgettable%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20because%20they%20were%20ruined%20because%20I%20didn't%20have%20the%20right%20documentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravel-documents-minors-not-parent-tsa-consent-form-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772892901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a1a950fd4fbd083f292f4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravel-documents-minors-not-parent-tsa-consent-form-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TSA%20doesn't%20always%20require%20IDs%20for%20minors%2C%20but%20I%20still%20travel%20with%20passports%20and%20consent%20forms%20for%20my%20godsons.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Indi