3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe'd%20stay%20in%20a%20five-star%20hotel%20in%20Cascais%2C%20a%20gorgeous%20seaside%20just%20outside%20of%20Lisbon.%20Our%20schedule%20was%20packed%20with%20fun%20stuff%20like%20a%20helicopter%20tour%2C%20high-end%20massages%2C%20and%20lunch%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-first-time-michelin-star-restaurant-eleven-madison-park-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMichelin-starred%20restaurant%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20beach.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20was%20locked%20in%2C%20and%20it%20felt%20far%20too%20late%20to%20cancel.%20So%2C%20a%20few%20days%20after%20the%20bombshell%20request%2C%20we%20went.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217112169-0e19-40b3-b0df-44baf7b3cc2b%5C%22%3EOur%20'perfect'%20getaway%20felt%20confusing%2C%20tense%2C%20and%20awkward%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20chairs%20around%20body%20of%20water%20in%20front%20of%20hotel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a9f56cd3e2f1aef36a1500%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20stayed%20in%20a%20beautiful%20hotel%20right%20along%20the%20beach.%3Cp%3EAlix%20Campbell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20embarked%20on%20the%20three-and-a-half-hour%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edrive%20to%20our%20hotel%2C%20I%20brought%20up%20all%20the%20exciting%20activities%20awaiting%20us%20whenever%20the%20silence%20became%20uncomfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20pictured%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-romantic-destinations-according-to-frequent-traveler-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eanniversary%20getaway%3C%2Fa%3E%20completely%20differently.%20I%20thought%20we'd%20be%20in%20a%20happy%20cloud%20of%20not%20having%20seen%20each%20other%20for%20weeks%2C%20ready%20for%20a%20little%20romantic%20adventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20we%20were%20stuck%20in%20this%20weird%20place.%20I%20didn't%20fully%20understand%20what%20was%20going%20on%20between%20us%2C%20and%20he%20wasn't%20fully%20able%20to%20communicate%20his%20feelings.%20Although%20he%20seemed%20to%20have%20made%20up%20his%20mind%20about%20splitting%2C%20I%20still%20believed%20we%20could%20work%20things%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20of%20our%20four-day%20trip%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20pretend%20that%20everything%20was%20fine%2C%20but%2C%20of%20course%2C%20I%20felt%20it%20wasn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20usual%20silly%20banter%20between%20us%20felt%20forced.%20When%20we%20sat%20in%20a%20restaurant%20after%20a%20full%20day%20of%20activities%2C%20we%20giddily%20chatted%20about%20the%20fancy%20dishes%20being%20served%20to%20us%2C%20but%20when%20we%20walked%20back%20to%20our%20hotel%20post-meal%2C%20we%20were%20mostly%20silent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20put%20a%20cherry%20on%20top%20of%20this%20awkwardness%2C%20the%20hotel%20surprised%20us%20with%20a%20bottle%20of%20Champagne%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmake-chocolate-dipped-strawberries-easy-way-review-photos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echocolate-covered%20strawberries%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20date%20of%20our%20anniversary.%20I%20didn't%20know%20whether%20to%20laugh%20or%20cry%20as%20a%20staff%20member%20wheeled%20these%20goodies%20into%20our%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20connection%20between%20us%20still%20felt%20undeniable%20%E2%80%94%20there%20were%20still%20the%20inside%20jokes%20we'd%20curated%20over%20the%20years%2C%20that%20familiarity%2C%20and%20a%20feeling%20of%20safety%20that%20I'd%20taken%20for%20granted%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20both%20seemed%20to%20cycle%20through%20a%20bunch%20of%20emotions%2C%20ping-ponging%20between%20feeling%20like%20strangers%20wildly%20attracted%20to%20each%20other%20(especially%20after%20a%20few%20cocktails)%20and%20a%20couple%20grappling%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20their%20relationship%20was%20broken.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20we%20got%20home%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20we'd%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Ftaking-a-break-in-a-relationship%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etake%20some%20time%20apart%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20moved%20out%20and%20stayed%20with%20friends%2C%20while%20I%20remained%20in%20our%20home%20looking%20after%20our%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22409cdc74-bf3e-4ce0-b622-0ab5e5d65c6a%5C%22%3ELooking%20back%2C%20I%20don't%20regret%20going%20on%20the%20trip%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Table%20set%20for%20dinner%20with%20view%20of%20beach%20behind%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a9f57afd4fbd083f299dc9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAt%20the%20Michelin-starred%20restaurant%20literally%20on%20the%20beach%3Cp%3EAlix%20Campbell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20after%20our%20vacation%2C%20we%20finally%20sat%20down%20together%20and%20really%20talked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20had%20more%20time%20to%20let%20everything%20settle%2C%20I%20reflected%20on%20our%20vacation%20during%20this%20turbulent%20time.%20I%20realized%20it%20was%20OK%20for%20me%20to%20feel%20confused%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20breakup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20acknowledge%20that%20although%20we%20laughed%20and%20had%20romantic%20moments%2C%20I%20felt%20disillusioned.%20I%20felt%20nostalgic%2C%20but%20I%20also%20noticed%20a%20rift%20between%20us%20that%20made%20me%20incredibly%20sad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe'd%20lost%20himself%20along%20the%20way%20as%20our%20relationship%20progressed%2C%20and%20whenever%20I%20noticed%20him%20withdrawing%20I%20wouldn't%20dig%20too%20deep%20because%20I%20was%20afraid%20he'd%20tell%20me%20something%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20hear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pressure%20built%20up%2C%20and%20this%20lack%20of%20communication%20led%20to%20the%20very%20issues%20we%20were%20trying%20to%20avoid%3A%20Me%2C%20being%20left%2C%20and%20him%2C%20having%20to%20deal%20with%20all%20of%20these%20emotions%20instead%20of%20running%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20on%20this%20trip%20was%20weird%20and%20uncomfortable%3B%20a%20desperate%20attempt%20to%20%26quot%3Bfix%26quot%3B%20us.%20It%20didn't.%20Instead%2C%20it%20provided%20the%20confined%20space%20away%20from%20home%20we%20needed%20to%20be%20confronted%20with%20issues%20we%20most%20likely%20would've%20kept%20avoiding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Cascais%2C%20I%20didn't%20know%20where%20our%20relationship%20would%20end%20up.%20Now%2C%20we're%20working%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdivorce-got-back-together-ex-husband-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efinalizing%20our%20divorce%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20believe%20it%20or%20not%2C%20we're%20on%20good%20terms.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20glad%20we%20went%20on%20the%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhusband-asked-for-divorce-trip-together-couples-vacation-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772892841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a9f4e8fd4fbd083f299da3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhusband-asked-for-divorce-trip-together-couples-vacation-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20was%20shocked%20when%20my%20husband%20asked%20for%20a%20divorce%20right%20before%20our%20anniversary%20trip.%20We%20went%20on%20vacation%20together%20anyway%20%E2%80%94it%20was%20messy%20but%20helped.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Alix%20Campbell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhusband-asked-for-divorce-trip-together-couples-vacation-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RSP's%20Balendra%20'Balen'%20Shah%20def