%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20cost%20is%20mounting%20for%20stranded%20travelers%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%3A%20'That's%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20we%20were%20not%20intending%20to%20spend'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225545%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Burj%20Khalifa%20skyline%20in%20Dubai%20obstructed%20by%20clouds.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69aabc24fd4fbd083f29a47c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223697%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20conflict%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20has%20left%20tens%20of%20thousands%20stranded%20in%20the%20UAE.%3Cp%3EChristopher%20Pike%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAir%20travel%20across%20the%20Middle%20East%20has%20been%20in%20a%20state%20of%20chaos%20since%20last%20Saturday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20travelers%20are%20racking%20up%20mounting%20hotel%20bills%20as%20they%20wait%20for%20a%20flight%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMany%20are%20confused%20about%20whether%20they%20will%20be%20saddled%20with%20or%20reimbursed%20for%20these%20bills.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEmilia%20Vasquez%2C%20a%20business%20development%20manager%20for%20Goodwill%2C%20landed%20in%20Dubai%20on%20Thursday%2C%20February%2026.%20She%20and%20her%206-year-old%20son%20had%20flown%20in%20to%20celebrate%20her%20birthday%2C%20and%20they%20were%20planning%20to%20stay%20until%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20later%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-us-general-rundown-opening-days-iran-attack-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20United%20States%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Israel%20launched%20strikes%20on%20Iran%2C%20and%20everything%20changed%20%E2%80%94%20across%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20airspaces%20shut%20down%2C%20airports%20closed%2C%20and%20thousands%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-stranded-middle-east-government-frustration-embassy-closed-iran-war-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etravelers%2C%20like%20Vasquez%2C%20found%20themselves%20stuck%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20navigated%20the%20logistics%20of%20getting%20stranded%2C%20they%20also%20faced%20another%20issue%3A%20the%20cost%20of%20getting%20stranded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20March%201%2C%20the%20General%20Civil%20Aviation%20Authority%20of%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20or%20GCAA%2C%20announced%20that%20the%20State%20would%20be%20bearing%20%26quot%3Ball%20hosting%20and%20accommodation%20costs%20for%20affected%20and%20stranded%20passengers.%26quot%3B%20The%20announcement%20did%20not%20specify%20how%20or%20when%20travelers%20would%20be%20reimbursed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Vasquez%2C%20the%20flight%20cancellations%20meant%20watching%20her%20hotel%20stay%20grow%20longer%20by%20the%20day.%20She%20was%20staying%20at%20Taj%20Dubai%20hotel%2C%20a%205-star%20hotel%20near%20the%20Dubai%20Mall%2C%20and%20spending%20about%20%24500%20a%20day%2C%20roughly%20%24300%20of%20which%20went%20to%20her%20hotel%20bill.%20As%20of%20Thursday%2C%20she%20had%20spent%20%246%2C800.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20bills%20racking%20up%20and%20no%20immediate%20money%20from%20the%20Emirati%20government%2C%20she%20was%20only%20a%20few%20thousand%20dollars%20away%20from%20her%20credit%20card%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20being%20responsible%20for%20paying%20for%20this%20hotel%2C%20the%20hotel%20literally%20telling%20us%20that%20if%20I%20cannot%20afford%20the%20hotel%20to%20leave%20and%20go%20somewhere%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20Vasquez%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Wednesday.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20feel%20safe%20to%20leave%20the%20hotel%20and%20go%20somewhere%20else.%20So%20I've%20been%20extending%20the%20days%20every%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-strikes-iran-what-to-do-american-middle-east-travel-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20airlines%20slowly%20resuming%20limited%20service%3C%2Fa%3E%20out%20of%20the%20region%2C%20Vasquez%20managed%20to%20leave%20Dubai%20on%20Friday%2C%20but%20for%20many%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-stranded-middle-east-government-frustration-embassy-closed-iran-war-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etravelers%20who%20remain%20on%20the%20ground%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bills%20continue%20to%20mount%20and%20confusion%20remains%20about%20whether%20they%20will%20be%20saddled%20with%20or%20reimbursed%20for%20these%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHave%20you%20been%20affected%20by%20the%20travel%20disruption%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%3F%20We%20want%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGet%20in%20touch%20with%20our%20reporters%3A%20Roya%2C%20in%20London%3A%20rshahidi%40insider.com%3B%20Josh%2C%20in%20London%3A%20jzitser%40insider.com%3B%20Maddie%2C%20in%20NYC%3A%20mberg%40insider.com.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Abu%20Dhabi%20and%20Dubai%20tourist%20ministries%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20General%20Civil%20Aviation%20Authority%20of%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fdc5e704-da4b-4875-8f56-6b9937957da2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'We're%20just%20trying%20to%20be%20as%20cheap%20as%20possible'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fate%20Show%20and%20her%20father%20standing%20in%20the%20Dubai%20Mall%20China%20Town%20with%20lanterns%20hanging%20behind%20them.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69aab67cfd4fbd083f29a46c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221020%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFate%20Show%20and%20her%20father%20in%20the%20Dubai%20Mall%20China%20Town.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Fate%20Show%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20well-heeled%20visitors%20paid%20six%20figures%20to%20get%20out%20of%20Dubai%2C%20others%20have%20been%20funding%20their%20extended%20stays%20through%20a%20mix%20of%20credit%20cards%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-stuck-doha-flight-to-nowhere-5-star-hotel-free-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eairline-provided%20vouchers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftourists-stranded-crowdfunding-pay-hotels-flights-middle-east-turmoil-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecrowdfunding%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Saturday%2C%20two%20of%20the%20region's%20biggest%20airlines%20%E2%80%94%20Emirates%20and%20Etihad%20%E2%80%94%20have%20resumed%20limited%20flight%20schedules%2C%20prioritizing%20existing%20customers.%20Qatar%20Airlines%20remained%20grounded%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fqatarairways%2Fstatus%2F2030210923051491702%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexception%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20limited%20flights%20to%20Doha.%20While%20the%20airlines%20haven't%20released%20guidance%20around%20obtaining%20hotel%20vouchers%2C%20several%20travelers%20said%20they've%20been%20able%20to%20receive%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFate%20Show%2C%20a%20Ph.D.%20student%2C%20was%20flying%20from%20Kuala%20Lumpur%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20to%20London%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewith%20her%20dad%20after%20seeing%20her%20family%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flunar-new-year-traditions-through-the-lens-of-three-photographers-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChinese%20New%20Year%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Their%20flight%20was%20scheduled%20to%20stop%20in%20Dubai%20on%20Saturday%20afternoon.%20When%20she%20arrived%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20she%20was%20met%20with%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmirates%20canceled%20their%20flight%20to%20London%20and%20provided%20a%20voucher%20to%20cover%20food%20and%20a%20hotel%20stay%20at%20the%20S%20Hotel%20Al%20Barsha%2C%20a%204-star%20hotel%20about%2020%20minutes%20from%20Dubai%20International%20Airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20voucher%20lasted%20four%20nights.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20after%20the%20voucher%20ran%20out%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethey%20switched%20hotels%20to%20the%20Hampton%20by%20Hilton%20Dubai%20Al%20Barsha%2C%20where%20they%20paid%20for%20their%20stay%20out%20of%20pocket.%20The%20room%2C%20with%20two%20single%20beds%2C%20cost%20%24112%20a%20night%20and%20included%20breakfast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20trying%20to%20limit%20additional%20spending%20on%20food%20to%20%2430%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20trying%20to%20do%20anything%20fancy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20just%20trying%20to%20be%20as%20cheap%20as%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20and%20her%20father%20tried%20to%20buy%20new%20tickets%20home%2C%20but%20said%20they%20were%20too%20expensive.%20On%20Friday%2C%20they%20moved%20to%20the%20Copthorne%20Hotel%20with%20their%20Emirates%20voucher.%20Her%20flight%20has%20been%20rescheduled%20for%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20Emirates%20hotel%20voucher%2C%20Show%20and%20her%20father%20have%20had%20to%20spend%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20during%20their%20unexpectedly%20extended%20stay%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20that's%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20we%20were%20not%20intending%20to%20spend%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20using%20a%20credit%20card%2C%20so%20we're%20hoping%20to%20be%20reimbursed%20by%20next%20month%20when%20we%20repay%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shanice%20Day%20in%20Dubai%20with%20an%20owl%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a6e48d1fb3fcb42648ccb5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShanice%20Day%20has%20managed%20to%20get%20a%20flight%20to%20Australia%20from%20Dubai%2C%20in%20order%20to%20make%20it%20back%20to%20the%20US.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Shanice%20Day%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShanice%20Day%2C%20a%20stylist%20from%20Houston%2C%20traveled%20to%20Dubai%20on%20February%2024%20to%20celebrate%20her%2030th%20birthday%20with%20her%20friend%20Remy%20Thomas%2C%20staying%20at%20the%20FIVE%20Luxe%20hotel%20near%20Jumeirah%20Beach.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETheir%20original%20flight%20home%20on%20March%201%20was%20canceled%2C%20along%20with%20subsequent%20rebookings%2C%20and%20they%20were%20left%20paying%20for%20their%20hotel%20out%20of%20pocket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Thomas%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftourists-stranded-crowdfunding-pay-hotels-flights-middle-east-turmoil-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estarted%20a%20GoFundMe%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20fundraise%20for%20their%20accommodation%20and%20flights%20back.%20As%20of%20Friday%2C%20the%20pair%20had%20raised%20%249%2C978%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eof%20their%20%2411%2C000%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDay%20managed%20to%20secure%20a%20flight%20out%20of%20Dubai%20to%20Sydney%20on%20Thursday.%20The%20following%20day%2C%20she%20flew%20from%20Sydney%20to%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20the%20penultimate%20leg%20of%20her%20round-the-world%20journey%20back%20to%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20probably%20get%20therapy%20after%20this%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Day%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20it's%20going%20to%20take%20me%20a%20while%20to%20build%20up%20the%20courage%20to%20travel%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShrihari%20Madhu%2C%20the%20manager%20of%20Coral%20Cove%2C%20which%20rents%20out%20three%20apartments%20in%20Dubai%20Marina%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20they%20have%20been%20helping%20tourists%20stranded%20by%20flight%20cancellations%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eby%20offering%20free%20accommodation%20or%20a%20base%20fee%20of%20around%20%2440%20a%20night.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOrdinarily%2C%20they%20rent%20their%20properties%20out%20for%20prices%20starting%20around%20%24110.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20travelers%20are%20reaching%20out%20because%20they%20need%20an%20immediate%20reliable%20place%20to%20stay%20while%20navigating%20these%20disruptions%2C%26quot%3B%20Madhu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMadhu%20said%20the%20three%20apartments%20are%20currently%20occupied%20by%20guests%20whose%20travel%20plans%20were%20canceled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c8872c4-9edc-42bc-9e0f-1f677d31e429%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20only%20thing%20more%20expensive%20than%20staying%20is%20leaving%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20as%20tensions%20escalated%20and%20airspaces%20across%20the%20region%20shut%20down%2C%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwealthy-people-dubai-abu-dhabi-chartering-planes-evacuate-middle-east-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewealthy%20travelers%20in%20the%20UAE%3C%2Fa%3E%20hired%20chauffeurs%20to%20drive%20them%20into%20Oman%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20The%20trips%20involved%20hours%20in%20the%20car%2C%20including%20long%20waits%20at%20border%20crossings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20they%20chartered%20private%20planes%2C%20spending%20upward%20of%20%24200%2C000%20to%20make%20it%20out%2C%20Ameerh%20Naran%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Vimana%20Private%20Jets%2C%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20demand%20to%20leave%20the%20region%20had%20started%20to%20tick%20up%20on%20Friday%2C%20when%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20conflict%20with%20Iran%20became%20more%20acute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20a%20clear%20emphasis%20on%20speed%20and%20certainty%20of%20departure%2C%20with%20many%20clients%20prioritizing%20the%20earliest%20viable%20routing%20rather%20than%20specific%20aircraft%20types%20or%20traditional%20preferences%2C%26quot%3B%20Naran%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20also%20seen%20increased%20demand%20for%20coordinated%20ground%20support%20to%20facilitate%20access%20to%20airports%20where%20airspace%20remains%20open.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmiddle-east-travel-disruption-hotel-bills-expenses-vouchers-who-pays-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772888798000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab299dd3e2f1aef36a26c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmiddle-east-travel-disruption-hotel-bills-expenses-vouchers-who-pays-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20travelers%20stranded%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20navigated%20the%20logistics%20of%20getting%20stranded%2C%20they%20also%20faced%20another%20issue%3A%20the%20cost%20of%20getting%20stranded.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mberg%40businessinsider.com%20(Madeline%20Berg%2CRoya%20Shahidi%2CAlexandra%20Karplus%2CPolly%20Thompson%2CJoshua%20Nelken-Zitser)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmiddle-east-travel-disruption-hotel-bills-expenses-vouchers-who-pays-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Neena%20Gupta%20drops%20video%20of%20her%201st%20TV%20show%3B%20netizens%20react%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772888714000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129215512%2Cimgsize-144684.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fneena-gupta-drops-a-video-of-her-first-tv-serial-for-a-channel-netizens-react-saying-woh-zamana-kya-din-the%2Farticleshow%2F129215512.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F129215512.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ENostalgia%20hit%20hard%20as%20veteran%20actress%20