0not%20be%20a%20Hollywood%20star%2C%20but%20her%20department%20spent%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavid-ellison-paramount-reorg-tech-new-streaming-features-execs-wbd-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebig%20studios%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20secretary%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20was%20ousted%20from%20her%20post%20on%20Thursday%2C%20following%20months%20of%20controversy%20over%20her%20handling%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fafl-cio-ice-raids-minnesota-day-truth-freedom-homeland-security-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eimmigration%20enforcement%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Trump's%20mass%20deportation%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20Noem's%20appearance%20before%20Congress%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Senator%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EJohn%20Kennedy%2C%20among%20other%20lawmakers%20from%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20political%20aisle%2C%20pressed%20Noem%20about%20the%20department's%20spending%20of%20taxpayer%20dollars%2C%20including%20a%20%24220%20million%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.propublica.org%2Farticle%2Fkristi-noem-dhs-ad-campaign-strategy-group%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ead%20contract%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ads%2C%20which%20Noem%20said%20were%20intended%20to%20encourage%20undocumented%20immigrants%20to%20leave%20the%20US%2C%20included%20footage%20of%20the%20now-former%20secretary%20riding%20a%20horse%20in%20front%20of%20Mount%20Rushmore%20while%20delivering%20stern%20messages%20about%20border%20enforcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawmakers%20scrutinized%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-wbd-deal-questions-regulatory-approval-timeline-netflix-david-ellison-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebidding%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20contracts%20behind%20the%20ad%20campaign%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20firms%20selected%2C%20raising%20questions%20about%20how%20taxpayer%20dollars