t%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFeria%20de%20las%20Flores%20silleteros%20parade%20in%20Medell%C3%ADn%2C%20Colombia.%3Cp%3ESergio%20Palacio%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJamali%20said%20the%20family%20is%20still%20adjusting%20to%20cultural%20differences%2C%20like%20how%20the%20country%20largely%20shuts%20down%20for%20holidays.%20She%20said%20it%20can%20make%20juggling%20work%20and%20childcare%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20take%20holidays%20really%20seriously%20here%2C%20and%20in%20January%2C%20almost%20all%20the%20daycares%20were%20closed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSince%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20both%20work%20for%20US-based%20clients%2C%20that%20was%20really%20hard%20to%20figure%20out%20childcare.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20to%20give%20ourselves%20grace%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BWe%20weren't%20going%20to%20have%20the%20same%20capacity%20for%20work.%20But%20that's%20also%20the%20beauty%20of%20coming%20here%20%E2%80%94%20we%20came%20for%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20lifestyle.%20This%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%20unexpected%20things%20we're%20adapting%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHaving%20a%20lower%20cost%20of%20living%20has%20improved%20their%20quality%20of%20life%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20take%20a%20selfie%20at%20a%20restaurant%2C%20surrounded%20by%20trees.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a75e431fb3fcb42648dcd8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJamali%20and%20her%20husband.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jennifer%20Jamali%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Jamali%2C%20a%20major%20upside%20of%20the%20move%20to%20Bogot%C3%A1%20has%20been%20financial.%20She%20said%20the%20family's%20monthly%20living%20expenses%20have%20dropped%20from%20about%20%247%2C000%20in%20Austin%20to%20roughly%20%242%2C000%20in%20Bogot%C3%A1.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20biggest%20savings%20have%20been%20on%20housing.%20They%20still%20own%20a%201%2C800-square-foot%2C%20four-bedroom%20home%20in%20Austin%20that%20has%20a%20mortgage%20of%20around%20%242%2C000%2C%20which%20they're%20continuing%20to%20rent%20out%20as%20a%20mid-term%20rental%20on%20Airbnb%20and%20Vrbo.%20But%20in%20Bogot%C3%A1%2C%20they%20live%20rent-free%20in%20a%20900-square-foot%20apartment%20that%20her%20in-laws%20invested%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20able%20to%20save%20more%2C%20and%20our%20cost%20of%20living%20is%20just%20much%20lower%2C%26quot%3B%20Jamali%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20stress%20as%20much%20about%20having%20a%20good%20month%20or%20a%20bad%20month%20financially.%20We're%20not%20trying%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20rising%20costs%20we%20dealt%20with%20in%20the%20US.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-florida-medellin-colombia-afford-life-of-luxury-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elower%20cost%20of%20living%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20have%20been%20able%20to%20work%20less%2C%20giving%20the%20family%20more%20time%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20a%20lot%20more%20active%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20because%20we're%20saving%20more%2C%20the%20pressure%20we%20put%20on%20ourselves%20has%20gone%20down%2C%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20is%20better%2C%20and%20we're%20having%20better%20experiences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHer%20family%20feels%20more%20connected%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20stands%20on%20a%20hillside%20surrounded%20by%20trees.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a75de9d3e2f1aef369ef1d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJamali%20in%20her%20in-laws%20backyard.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jennifer%20Jamali%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-back-to-colombia-after-21-years-us-better-life-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMoving%20to%20Bogot%C3%A1%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20brought%20Jamali's%20family%20closer%20together.%20Her%20in-laws%20are%20just%20a%20short%20walk%20away%2C%20which%20means%20regular%20visits%20and%20extra%20childcare%20help%20when%20they%20need%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20in-laws%20living%20in%20the%20mountains%2C%20Jamali%20and%20her%20husband%20also%20have%20a%20place%20to%20go%20when%20they%20want%20to%20unplug%2C%20and%20they'll%20sometimes%20spend%20up%20to%20a%20week%20at%20their%20home.%20Being%20outside%20and%20spending%20time%20in%20nature%20%E2%80%94%20a%20contrast%20to%20Austin's%20concrete%20sprawl%20%E2%80%94%20has%20helped%20her%20feel%20more%20at%20ease%20and%20more%20creative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-grandma-refuses-babysit-her-kids-know-not-to-ask-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupport%20from%20my%20in-laws%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20safety%20I%20feel%20here%2C%20I've%20been%20thriving%20in%20Bogot%C3%A1%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20helped%20my%20mental%20health%20and%20my%20life%20in%20so%20many%20ways.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-texas-to-bogota-colombia-cheaper-cost-of-living-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772884561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a85039fd4fbd083f297f38%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-texas-to-bogota-colombia-cheaper-cost-of-living-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jennifer%20Jamali%20said%20there's%20a%20lot%20to%20love%20about%20Bogota%2C%20Colombia%2C%20but%20the%20best%20part%20