f299cae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAlina%20Rudya%2FBell%20Collective%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20post%20originally%20appeared%20in%20the%20BI%20Today%20newsletter.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20sign%20up%20for%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Finsider-today%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20daily%20newsletter%20here%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef84679e-5101-4303-beb5-fc75bc92b8c0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EForget%20happy%20hour.%20Try%20playing%20hooky.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20it!%20Reparations%20for%20our%20pain%20and%20suffering%2C%26quot%3B%20my%20friend%2C%20Lauren%20Grove%2C%20texted%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20right%20after%20a%20February%20blizzard%20had%20dumped%20more%20than%2012%20inches%20of%20snow%20over%20the%20Tri-State%20area%2C%20and%20with%20her%20kids%20being%20the%20same%20age%20as%20mine%20%E2%80%94%20busy%206-%20and%203-year-olds%20(and%20did%20I%20mention%2C%20they're%20boys!)%20%E2%80%94%20we%20were%20in%20desperate%20need%20of%20a%20break.%20So%20Lauren%20invited%20our%20mom%20group%20chat%20to%20play%20hooky%20from%20work%20that%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20person%20who%20prides%20herself%20on%20productivity%20and%20who's%20never%20met%20a%20to-do%20list%20I%20didn't%20enjoy%20tackling%2C%20playing%20hooky%20didn't%20immediately%20appeal%20to%20me.%20Still%2C%20Lauren%20assured%20me%20it%20was%20only%20an%20hour%20during%20the%20lunch%20break%2C%20and%20I'd%20still%20make%20it%20in%20time%20to%20pick%20up%20my%20children%20from%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFine.%20It%20felt%20like%20a%20no-brainer%2C%20especially%20since%20one%20of%20my%20goals%20this%20year%20is%20to%20be%20more%20intentional%20about%20creating%20community%20after%20my%20family%20and%20I%20moved%20post-pandemic%20to%20a%20sleepy%20New%20Jersey%20suburb.%20And%20overindexing%20on%20work%20has%20been%20known%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-deal-with-stress-burnout-work-mental-health-professional-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecause%20burnout%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20higher%20rates%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-your-job-is-making-you-miserable-2016-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanxiety%20and%20depression%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20along%20with%20affecting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-have-most-productive-day-based-on-sleep-schedule-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esleep%20quality%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20the%20only%20one.%20Although%20the%20hum%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmodern-loneliness%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20loneliness%20epidemic%3C%2Fa%3E%20isn't%20as%20loud%20in%20the%20headlines%2C%20many%20are%20still%20feeling%20the%20effects%20of%20increased%20solitude.%20We're%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floneliness-epidemic-decline-in-third-places-friends-parks-community-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espending%20less%20time%20with%20friends%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20years%2C%20Americans%20averaged%20about%206.5%20hours%20a%20week%20with%20friends.%20Between%202014%20and%202019%2C%20that%20number%20plunged%20by%2037%25%2C%20to%20just%204%20hours.%20The%20year%202014%20coincides%20with%20a%20rise%20in%20smartphone%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20that%20community%20doesn't%20just%20happen%3B%20like%20most%20things%20in%20life%2C%20it%20takes%20effort.%20And%20there%20are%20only%20so%20many%20coffee%20shops%20and%20libraries%20you%20can%20go%20to%20without%20experiencing%20third-space%20fatigue.%20Plus%2C%20this%20hooky%20party%20felt%20low%20stakes%3A%20It%20was%20time-constrained%20with%20no%20expectation%20to%20hang%20out%20late.%20I%20also%20didn't%20have%20to%20hire%20a%20babysitter%20to%20enjoy%20it%20since%20it%20was%20midday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20party%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20an%20amazing%20time%2C%20by%20the%20way%2C%20complete%20with%20food%20and%20line%20dancing%20%E2%80%94%20I%20asked%20Lauren%2C%20the%20chief%20experience%20architect%20at%20event%20design%20firm%20The%20Grant%20Access%2C%20what%20inspired%20her%20to%20host%20the%20hooky%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20is%20crazy%20right%20now%2C%20and%20all%20we%20truly%20have%20is%20community.%20We%20have%20to%20cultivate%20it%20and%20feed%20into%20it%3B%20not%20just%20by%20engaging%20online%20but%20by%20seeing%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BThis%20hooky%20party%20served%20as%20an%20opportunity%20for%20us%20to%20close%20our%20laptops%20and%20find%20joy%20with%20the%20people%20we%20love.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20I%20got%20home%2C%20my%20to-do%20list%20was%20waiting%20for%20me%2C%20but%20at%20least%20I%20got%20a%20midday%20reminder%20that%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20do%20life%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-saturday-newsletter-playing-hooky-lessons-in-community-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772883661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a9ebf21fb3fcb4264901f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-saturday-newsletter-playing-hooky-lessons-in-community-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20this%20Saturday%20edition%20of%20Business%20Insider%20Today%2C%20we're%20talking%20about%20taking%20time%20off%20from%20work%20and%20finding%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jmckenzie%40businessinsider.com%20(Joi-Marie%20McKenzie)