20bought%20sports%20investing%20experts%20Arctos%20Partners%20for%20%241.4%20billion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKKR's%20co-CEO%20Scott%20Nuttall%20explained%20how%20a%20deal%20a%20decade%20ago%20led%20to%20KKR's%20acquisition.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20outlined%20how%20KKR%20and%20Arctos%20would%20build%20out%20a%20business%20buying%20stakes%20in%20private%20equity%20funds.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EKKR's%20%241.4%20billion%20acquisition%20of%20Arctos%20Partners%20traces%20back%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20to%20a%20relationship%20that%20began%20long%20before%20Arctos%20even%20existed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20known%20Ian%20Charles%2C%20the%20founder%2C%20for%20a%20long%20time%3A%20a%20decade%20plus%2C%26quot%3B%20Nuttall%20said%20at%20Bloomberg's%20Invest%20conference%20on%20Wednesday%20as%20he%20got%20into%20the%20backstory%20of%20the%20deal%20announced%20last%20month.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20KKR%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20secondaries%20specialist%20to%20help%20free%20up%20capital%20and%20worked%20with%20Charles%2C%20who%20at%20the%20time%20worked%20at%20Landmark%20Partners%2C%20a%20major%20secondaries%20investor%20later%20acquired%20by%20Ares.%20The%20collaboration%20helped%20lay%20the%20groundwork%20for%20KKR's%20healthcare%20and%20tech%20growth%20platforms%2C%20which%20now%20manage%20more%20than%20%2417%20billion%2C%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20know%2C%20sometimes%20you%20meet%20somebody%20and%20say%2C%20wow%2C%20they're%20really%20capable%2C%20and%20you%20would%20love%20to%20have%20him%20as%20part%20of%20our%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20Nuttall%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20that%20kind%20of%20a%20moment.%20Sadly%2C%20he%20worked%20somewhere%20else%20at%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharles%20went%20on%20to%20cofound%20Arctos%20in%202019%2C%20and%20the%20firm%20has%20fast%20become%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20players%20in%20sports%20investing.%20It%20is%20the%20only%20firm%20with%20private%20equity%20stakes%20in%20all%20five%20major%20men's%20professional%20sports%20leagues%20in%20the%20US%2C%20including%20ownership%20stakes%20in%20the%20LA%20Dodgers%2C%20the%20Golden%20State%20Warriors%2C%20and%20the%20Buffalo%20Bills.%20They've%20also%20invested%20in%20international%20powerhouses%20such%20as%20the%20Aston%20Martin%20F1%20team%2C%20Liverpool%20FC%2C%20and%20Paris%20Saint-Germain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESports%20have%20become%20a%20major%20investment%20thesis%20in%20private%20equity%2C%20with%20a%20record%20%2423.6%20billion%20in%20sports%20franchise%20acquisitions%20and%20%246.3%20billion%20in%20sports%20services%20acquisitions%20in%20the%20first%20three%20quarters%20of%202025%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spglobal.com%2Fmarket-intelligence%2Fen%2Fnews-insights%2Farticles%2F2025%2F10%2Fprivate-equity-deal-value-in-sports-services-hits-8-year-high-of-6b-93884455%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20Global%20Market%20Intelligence%20Data%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKKR%20has%20yet%20to%20buy%20any%20sports%20franchises%2C%20but%20has%20made%20investments%20in%20cheerleading%20apparel%20company%20Varsity%20Brands%2C%20and%20high%20school%20streaming%20platform%20PlayOn!%20Sports%2C%20and%20previously%20invested%20in%20FanDuel%20and%20the%20UFC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20Charles%20co-founded%20Arctos%2C%20the%20relationship%20developed%20%26quot%3Borganically%20from%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nuttall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20we%20started%20looking%20at%20what%20they%20were%20doing%20and%20bec%2Cause%20of%20our%20relationship%2C%20we%20just%20were%20comparing%20notes%2C%26quot%3B%20Nuttall%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%2C%20they%20would%20call%20for%20advice%2C%20we'd%20call%20them%2C%20get%20their%20thoughts%20on%20the%20markets%2C%20that%20kind%20of%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20KKR%20looked%20to%20finally%20add%20a%20stake-buying%20business%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bone%20thing%20we%20do%20not%20have%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20firm%2C%20Nuttall%20said%2C%20Arctos%20made%20sense.%20KKR%20evaluated%20other%20firms%20in%20this%20space%20as%20they%20went%20to%20market%2C%20but%20Arctos%2C%20which%20buys%20stakes%20in%20other%20private%20markets%20firms%2C%20was%20the%20right%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20dominance%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20attractive%26quot%3B%20sports%20field%2C%20combined%20with%20their%20%26quot%3Bsecondaries%20background%26quot%3B%20opens%20up%20opportunities%20in%20not%20just%20sports%20franchises%20but%20also%20%26quot%3Breal%20estate%2C%20securitizing%20media%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BGP%20solutions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20combination%20of%20the%20right%20relationship%20fit%20and%20their%20former%20expertise%20made%20it%20the%20right%20place%20to%20%26quot%3Bbuild%20secondaries%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Nuttall%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkkr-arctos-sports-bet-decade-old-relationship-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772883241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab3944fd4fbd083f29b253%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkkr-arctos-sports-bet-decade-old-relationship-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20story%20of%20KKR's%20acquisition%20of%20Arctos%20Partners%20began%20years%20before%20the%20firm%20was%20founded%2C%20when%20one%20founder%20impressed%20KKR%20as%20a%20deal%20counterparty.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22anicoll%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Nicoll)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkkr-arctos-sports-bet-decade-old-relationship-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nairobi%20flash%20floods%20kill%20more%20than%2020%20people%20and%20cause%20widespread%20airpo