20small%20community%20centre%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20OSCAR%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScaling%20up%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy.%20Donors%20asked%20for%20registration%20papers%2C%20tax%20exemptions%2C%20and%20audited%20accounts.%20So%20in%202010%2C%20Ashok%20formally%20registered%20the%20OSCAR%20Foundation.%20Convincing%20parents%20was%20harder.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20accused%20me%20of%20spoiling%20their%20children.%20Friends%20mocked%20me%20for%20chasing%20what%20they%20thought%20was%20a%20hobby%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20persistence%20brought%20change.%20Children%20who%20once%20skipped%20school%20started%20attending%20regularly%20because%20of%20the%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20rule%3A%20%E2%80%98No%20School%2C%20No%20Football%E2%80%99.%20Barriers%20of%20caste%20and%20religion%20dissolved%20on%20the%20field%2C%20replaced%20by%20teamwork%2C%20discipline%2C%20and%20respect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-4-1757076545.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rathod%20aims%20to%20enrich%20children%E2%80%99s%20lives%20with%20the%20discipline%2C%20teamwork%2C%20and%20hope%20derived%20from%20football.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-4-1757076545.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-4-1757076545-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-4-1757076545-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-4-1757076545-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-4-1757076