s%20resulted%20in%20a%20steep%20rise%20in%20regular%20attendance%2C%20from%20fewer%20than%2030%20to%20100%20students%20within%20a%20month%20of%20her%20intensive%20community%20engagement.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1-1757060631.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1-1757060631-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1-1757060631-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1-1757060631-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1-1757060631-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496798%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHer%20efforts%20resulted%20in%20a%20rise%20in%20regular%20attendance%2C%20from%20fewer%20than%2030%20to%20100%20students%20within%20a%20month%20of%20her%20intensive%20community%20engagement.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20empty%20classrooms%20to%20crowded%20mornings%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20day%20begins%20before%20dawn.%20By%208%20AM%2C%20Sangeeta%20is%20already%20at%20the%20school%20gate%2C%20greeting%20children%20who%20walk%20in%20barefoot%2C%20their%20satchels%20bouncing%20against%20their%20backs.%20The%20sight%20warms%20her%20now%2C%20but%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20always%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COut%20of%20130%20children%20enrolled%2C%20fewer%20than%2030%20attended%20regularly%20when%20I%20first%20joined%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20remembers%20her%20frustration.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20just%20sit%20inside%20the%20classroom%20and%20wait.%20So%20after%20school%20hours%2C%20I%20would%20go%20door%20to%20door%20in%20the%20afternoons.%20I%20sat%20with%20parents%2C%20explained%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F364214%2Fteachers-day-radhakrishnan-abdul-kalam-jyotirao-savitribai-phule-history-pics-gopal-krishna-gokhale%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhy%20education%20mattered%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20why%20it%20was%20worth%20sending%20their%20children%20to%20school%20instead%20of%20making%20them%20work.%20Many%20of%20these%20children%20did%20odd%20jobs%20and%20spent%20their%20earnings%20on%20tobacco%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CConvincing%20parents%20and%20children%20was%20a%20battle.%20I%20begged%20at%20times%2C%20I%20reasoned%20at%20others%2C%20and%20I%20kept%20asking%20them%20to%20send%20their%20children%20to%20school%20at%20least%20one%20more%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlowly%2C%20her%20persistence%20paid%20off.%20Within%20a%20month%2C%20attendance%20rose%20to%20100%20students.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20an%20easy%20victory%3B%20it%20meant%20knocking%20on%20doors%20daily%2C%20challenging%20traditions%20of%20child%20labour%2C%20and%20winning%20the%20trust%20of%20parents%20who%20had%20never%20experienced%20the%20benefits%20of%20education%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETeaching%20beyond%20textbooks%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20children%20began%20attending%20regularly%2C%20a%20new%20challenge%20emerged%3A%20holding%20their%20attention.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1757060638.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sangeeta%20employs%20innovative%20teaching%20methods%2C%20such%20as%20incorporating%20songs%20and%20interactive%20activities%20to%20make%20learning%20enjoyable.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1757060638.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1757060638-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1757060638-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1757060638-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1757060638-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496799%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESangeeta%20employs%20innovative%20teaching%20methods%2C%20such%20as%20incorporating%20songs%20and%20interactive%20activities%20to%20make%20learning%20enjoyable.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConventional%20lesson%20plans%20fell%20flat.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20children%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20just%20sit%20and%20listen%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20brightened%20up%20when%20I%20told%20stories%2C%20sang%20songs%2C%20or%20played%20games%20with%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20began%20using%20folk%20tales%2C%20riddles%2C%20and%20interactive%20activities%20to%20make%20learning%20enjoyable.%20Over%20time%2C%20the%20children%20started%20participating%20eagerly.%20They%20even%20role-played%20as%20teachers%2C%20doctors%2C%20and%20police%20officers.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20classroom%20filled%20with%20laughter%20and%20energy.%20When%20the%20children%20laugh%20and%20play%2C%20they%20learn%20without%20even%20realising%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Sangeeta%2C%20these%20moments%20are%20priceless.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20child%20tells%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20want%20to%20be%20a%20teacher%20like%20you%2C%E2%80%99%20my%20heart%20swells%20with%20pride.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBalancing%20two%20worlds%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%20school%2C%20Sangeeta%20is%20a%20mother%20and%20wife.%20Married%20in%20Azamgarh%2C%20with%20her%20parental%20home%20in%20Raebareli%2C%20she%20balances%20household%20responsibilities%20with%20teaching.%20Her%20son%2C%20now%20seven%2C%20once%20had%20clashing%20school%20timings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sangeeta%20fulfills%20multiple%20roles%20from%20mentor%20to%20friend%2C%20crucially%20adapting%20her%20skills%20to%20meet%20the%20varied%20needs%20of%20her%20students.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496803%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESangeeta%20fulfills%20multiple%20roles%20from%20mentor%20to%20friend%2C%20crucially%20adapting%20her%20skills%20to%20meet%20the%20varied%20needs%20of%20her%20students.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20tough%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20admits.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20never%20let%20my%20struggles%20show%20in%20front%20of%20my%20students.%20They%20deserve%20my%20full%20attention.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMore%20than%20a%20teacher%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESangeeta%E2%80%99s%20role%20extends%20beyond%20academics.%20She%20eats%20midday%20meals%20sitting%20cross-legged%20with%20the%20children.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20they%20see%20me%20eating%20from%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20plate%20as%20theirs%2C%20they%20feel%20I%20am%20one%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20seasonal%20fevers%2C%20she%20keeps%20basic%20medicines%20in%20the%20staffroom.%20%E2%80%9COn%20days%20when%20rice%20is%20served%20in%20the%20midday%20meal%2C%20I%20avoid%20giving%20it%20to%20sick%20children%2C%20as%20rice%20is%20believed%20to%20aggravate%20colds.%20Instead%2C%20I%20share%20my%20tiffin%20with%20them%20before%20giving%20medicine%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20school%20day%20officially%20ends%20at%202%20PM%2C%20but%20the%20work%20continues%20%E2%80%94%20preparing%20lesson%20plans%2C%20completing%20paperwork%2C%20and%20visiting%20families%20whose%20children%20miss%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20true%20reward%20of%20teaching%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Sangeeta%2C%20teaching%20has%20never%20been%20just%20a%20job.%20It%20is%20a%20mission.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20villages%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F261821%2Finspiring-uttarakhand-teacher-pandemic-village-students-lockdown%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteaching%20is%20as%20much%20about%20care%20%3C%2Fa%3Eas%20it%20is%20about%20books.%20You%20have%20to%20build%20trust%2C%20spark%20curiosity%2C%20and%20show%20children%20that%20education%20can%20change%20their%20lives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20pauses%2C%20then%20adds%20softly%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%2C%20the%20classrooms%20were%20empty%2C%20and%20I%20cried.%20Today%2C%20those%20rooms%20echo%20with%20chatter%2C%20laughter%2C%20and%20learning.%20That%20is%20my%20biggest%20reward.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757068200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%